    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, serving as a reliable daily driver while showing expected signs of its history. On the exterior, you will find several noticeable scratches and a few minor door dings consistent with age. The interior is functional but exhibits some wear, including slight fading on the upholstery and minor stains on the carpet. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may benefit from a routine tune-up in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
