    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all tinkerers and project lovers! This vehicle is the ultimate blank canvas for someone who enjoys a hands-on restoration project. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and shows its age, it offers a fantastic opportunity to get into a car at an incredibly low price point. Bring your tools and your vision to bring this one back to life!",
