    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint is still vibrant, though you'll find a few minor door dings and some light scuffing on the rear bumper from normal use. Inside, the leather seats are well-preserved with only slight creasing on the driver's side. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, and all electronics are fully functional. It\u2019s a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid car that has many miles left to give.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
