    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to an exacting standard that satisfies even the most fastidious collector. Every aspect of this motorcar remains in showroom condition, reflecting a legacy of meticulous preservation and absolute mechanical integrity. This offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unrivaled quality and provenance.",
