      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle represents the zenith of its class, preserved in showroom condition with an uncompromising commitment to maintenance. Every mechanical component and aesthetic detail adheres to the highest standards of excellence, offering a definitive driving experience for the discerning professional. An investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
